These are Puzzles for 1x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, chess, backgammon, bridge
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |    2     |     3      |   4    |      5       |
| Game   | whist | mah-jongg | chess | bridge | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, spy, comedy, family, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | fantasy | spy | western | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, cola, tea, iced-tea, juice
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3    |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea | cola | juice | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-1-4::.
