2. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |  1   |   2    |     3      |      4      |   5    |
| City   | boston | venice | marseilles | prague | berlin |

